 TIP: 70
 Title: Payment Protocol Implementation for Termucoin Infrastructure
 Author: AresCyu <areshin@proton.me>
 Status: Draft
 Type: Standards Track
 Created: 2026-06-18

== Abstract ==
This document outlines the custom implementation of the Payment Protocol for the Termucoin blockchain ecosystem.

== PaymentDetails/PaymentRequest Specification ==
To maintain independence from other directory services, Termucoin adopts a dynamic network identification strategy:
* '''Network Identification:''' Instead of relying on hardcoded strings, Termucoin nodes utilize the unique genesis block hash.
* '''Validation Logic:''' Payment requests must contain a metadata field "genesis" which the client wallet MUST verify against its local chainparams.

== Security Considerations ==
The protocol enforces strict origin verification to eliminate the risk of "replay attacks".

